1954;;The Outcast;;American;;William Witney;;John Derek, Joan Evans, Jim Davis;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Outcast_(1954_film);;Jet Cosgrave (John Derek) has been cheated out of his inheritance by his crooked uncle, Maj. Linton Cosgrave (Jim Davis) and outcast from the community. Jet tries to clear his name and win back his father’s ranch by hiring some gunmen. Along the way he falls for Judy Polsen (Joan Evans) and also flirts with his uncle’s fiancee.